 (Hijau \emdash  On Schedule), }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs72\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af31501\insrsid15757303 \hich\af1\dbch\af31501\loch\f1 0.85 \u8804  SPI < 0.95}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15757303
 (Kuning \emdash  Warning), dan }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs72\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af31501\insrsid15757303 \hich\af1\dbch\af31501\loch\f1 SPI < 0.85}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15757303
